你能够调用以下的API:
[['ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles', {'name': 'ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles', 'description': 'This function searches for research articles based on a specific topic and date.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the research articles, e.g., financial technology impact on banking.'}, {'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date from which to search for the latest articles.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching research articles, each with a title, author, and publication date.'}]}], ['ReportRetrieval.get_report', {'name': 'ReportRetrieval.get_report', 'description': 'This function retrieves a specific report based on the bank name and date.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}, {'name': 'date', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The date of the report.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'The detailed report including financial technology applications and impact analysis.'}]}], ['BankDataAccess.get_real_time_data', {'name': 'BankDataAccess.get_real_time_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves real-time business data for a specific bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Real-time business data including transactions, balances, and volumes.'}]}], ['PartnerInfo.get_partners', {'name': 'PartnerInfo.get_partners', 'description': 'This function retrieves information about financial technology partners for a specific bank.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'partners', 'description': 'A list of financial technology partners, including names and partnership details.'}]}], ['Consultancy.get_transformation_advice', {'name': 'Consultancy.get_transformation_advice', 'description': 'This function provides business transformation advice for a specific bank based on current financial technology trends.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'bankName', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The name of the bank.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'Strategic advice and recommendations for business transformation.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles` 并传入 `topic` 和 `date`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "ResearchArticleSearch.find_articles",
    "args": "{'topic': 'financial technology impact on banking', 'date': '2024-01-01'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
